OL,7,FA report into the circumstances that
OL,8,Fled to the death of Darlington toddler
OL,9,FCharlie Roberts has highlighted a lack
OL,10,Fof "professional curiosity" about his
OL,11,Fmother and her partner - the man who
OL,12,Fmurdered him.
OL,14,FCharlie was 22-months-old when he died
OL,15,Ffrom multiple injuries inflicted on
OL,16,Fhim by Christopher Stockton.
