OL,7,FStockton was jailed for life at
OL,8,FTeesside Crown Court earlier this
OL,9,Fyear. Charlie's mother, Paula Roberts,
OL,10,Fwas jailed for four years after
OL,11,Fadmitting neglect.
OL,13,FDarlington Safeguarding Partnership
OL,14,Ffound there had not been enough
OL,15,Fknowledge or understanding of her
OL,16,Fmental health difficulties.
OL,18,FThe report also found:
