OL,3,CReport finds 'lack of professional
OL,4,Ccuriosity' about murdered toddler's
OL,5,Cmother
OL,7,FStockton, 38, was in sole charge of
OL,8,FCharlie Roberts when he suffered an
OL,9,Funsurvivable head injury. He had moved
OL,10,Fin with Roberts and her son just seven
OL,11,Fdays earlier.
OL,13,FDuring the trial, Paula Roberts, 41,
OL,14,Fadmitted that she was suspicious
OL,15,Fenough about Stockton that she set up
OL,16,Fa spy camera above her son's cot.
OL,18,FBut she stayed in a relationship with
OL,19,Fhim, even after she voiced her
OL,20,Fconcerns about Stockton to her brother.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
